---
title: Shrimp and Chicken Noodle Bowl with Beans and Bok Choy
description: The base of this fantastic stir-fry is chow mein noodles! Tonight they are paired with chicken, shrimp and a sweet and salty sauce. Don't be afraid to slurp and enjoy each bite!
